data.description: Looking for an ALL brick, super clean, adorable rancher on almost 1/2 an acre in the city of Frederick? You found it. Beautiful updated kitchen with granite, backsplash and newer SS appliances - the dishwasher and refrigerator are new in 2024. Detached 2 car garage and driveway parking included. This home offers a spacious, level backyard that is fully fenced (maintenance free too) and is great for hosting your backyard BBQs and  parties on the new paver patio with pavilion. Finished basement with new flooring, additional 1/2 bath and electric fireplace. Basement has fire retardant sound proofing between floors. See the list of all the updates in the disclosures. Convenient to downtown, shopping and commuter routes. NO HOA!
